OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with rain in the south
OL,6,Fbecoming brighter as showers build
OL,7,Fthrough the morning. These showers
OL,8,Fwill become slow moving and heavy in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FBright spells and showers,
OL,12,Fthese becoming less frequent during
OL,13,Fthe evening. Clear spells increase for
OL,14,Fa time from late evening but cloud and
OL,15,Frain spread northeast later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FEarly cloud and rain soon
OL,18,Fclear northeast to leave the morning
OL,19,Fdry with sunny spells. The odd shower
OL,20,Fwill develop during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
