OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry at
OL,6,Ffirst, cloud, rain soon push northeast
OL,7,FSaturday. Rain becomes heavy in the
OL,8,Fsouth Sunday, clearing northeast early
OL,9,FMonday, becoming drier, brighter in
OL,10,Fthe afternoon.
